    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <div1>
                <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01817.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline><date when="1870-01-14">January 14, 1870</date></dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Walt Whitman</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I received your <choice>
                        <sic>vary</sic>
                        <corr>very</corr>
                    </choice> kind Letter and picture and am <choice>
                        <sic>vary</sic>
                        <corr>very</corr>
                    </choice> glad to hear from you. I <choice>
                        <sic>all so</sic>
                        <corr>also</corr>
                    </choice> Received your <choice>
                        <sic>vary</sic>
                        <corr>very</corr>
                    </choice> kind Papers, and have <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high"
                        resp="#nnk">taken</unclear> great pains to lay them away to look at some future time, but
                    the book I have never seen.</p>
                <p>Well now I will tell you about my mother. She sits in her chair <choice>
                        <sic>kniting</sic>
                        <corr>knitting</corr>
                    </choice> a pair of <choice>
                        <sic>mitens</sic>
                        <corr>mittens</corr>
                    </choice>. She says that she has a great <choice>
                        <sic>angsity</sic>
                        <corr>anxiety</corr>
                    </choice> to See you my father would like to see you also. My brother <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#ak" cert="low">is enquiring</unclear> I we
                    could all meet you 
                    
                    <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01817.004_large.jpg"
                        type="verso"/> 
                    
                    with a <choice>
                        <sic>harty</sic>
                        <corr>hearty</corr>
                    </choice> welcome.</p>
                <p>Mother has a very bad cold at <choice>
                        <sic>praisent</sic>
                        <corr>present</corr>
                    </choice>, the rest of us are <choice>
                        <sic>usaly</sic>
                        <corr>usually</corr>
                    </choice> well.</p>
                <p>I will send you one dollar to get some pictures with the picture you sent me of
                    your self I take a good look at it every now and then. I thank you <choice>
                        <sic>vary</sic>
                        <corr>very</corr>
                    </choice> much for the last one you sent, the views that you sent me are to be of the
                    public buildings of the city. I expect to start for Kansas next Tuesday but my
                        <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word" unit="chars" quantity="7"/> had to
                    postpone it for a few days on the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low"
                        resp="#nnk">account</unclear> of death in the family</p>
                <p>If you write soon I shall get it</p>
                <p>I expect tonight some friend here to make an evening call. You will <choice>
                        <sic>pleas</sic>
                        <corr>please</corr>
                    </choice> excuse me from writing as I wish to have some room for my father as he said he
                    would finish this. So fare <choice>
                        <sic>the</sic>
                        <corr>thee</corr>
                    </choice> my Dear Walt do not forget to address Williamson, Wayne Co. NY</p>
                <p><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">Much</unclear>
                    <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">respected</unclear>
                    <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words" unit="chars" quantity="6"/></p>
                <p>Friend W Whitman it is with the greatest pleasure I attempt to write a few lines
                    to fill out Alfred's letter we all feel a good the warmest affection for you for
                    you very great <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#ak" cert="medium">poems have</unclear> conferred on us in writing 
                    
                    <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.01817.003_large.jpg" type="verso"/> 
                    
                    to us when our son Alfred was
                    sick among strangers and among strangers we have formed a great desire to see you
                    and have a good and friendly talk. We did think that you would start out in the
                    bad weather and get out of the city and see us but now my boy is a going to <choice>
                        <sic>Kansis</sic>
                        <corr>Kansas</corr>
                    </choice> to live he expects to start for Kansas with some of our neighbours
                    next Tuesday a week to settle perhaps you may think it not <choice>
                        <sic>whorth</sic>
                        <corr>worth</corr>
                    </choice> a while to come and see us but we are very anxious to see you if you
                    think you can <choice>
                        <sic>posibly</sic>
                        <corr>possibly</corr>
                    </choice> come have <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words" unit="chars"
                        quantity="7"/> here of 130 acres 3 <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low"
                        resp="#nnk">horses</unclear>
                    <gap reason="illegible" extent="one digit" unit="chars" quantity="1"/> two year
                    old colts 9 cows
                    and expect 4 more in the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#nnk"
                        >spring</unclear> (that is 4 heifers come in <gap reason="illegible"
                        extent="two words" unit="chars" quantity="5"/> on the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#ak">next</unclear> steer) 
                    
                    <pb xml:id="leaf003r" facs="loc.01817.005_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                    
                    <fw place="top">(continued for want of room)</fw> and a lot of <choice>
                        <sic>poltry</sic>
                        <corr>poultry</corr>
                    </choice> such as turkeys Ducks and chickens</p>
                <p>Oh I had a daughter last <choice>
                        <abbr>aug</abbr>
                        <expan>August</expan>
                    </choice> a year ago and she lives with us yet but I expect to be able <unclear
                        reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">leave</unclear> with her in a few
                    days she <choice>
                        <sic>ways</sic>
                        <corr>weighs</corr>
                    </choice> about 100 lbs and is as handsome as a picture I think I will have her
                    picture before she goes and I will send you one</p>
                <p>please <choice>
                        <sic>except</sic>
                        <corr>accept</corr>
                    </choice> our thanks for past favours.</p>
                <p>Mrs Pratt send you her respects in particular</p>
                <p>Please write soon to your unworthy friends</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>John B. Pratt</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p> P.O. Williamson<lb/><unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk"
                            >Wayne</unclear> Co,<lb/>NY </p>
                </postscript>
            </div1>
            
            <div1>
                <pb xml:id="leaf004r" facs="loc.01817.006_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Walt Whitman</salute>
                    <salute>Dear Friend</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I am now at <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">my</unclear>
                    own home but have
                    not got my discharge yet. I left Washington on <choice>
                        <sic>trans furr</sic>
                        <corr>transfer</corr>
                    </choice> to <choice>
                            <sic>rochester</sic>
                            <corr>Rochester</corr>
                        </choice>.</p>
                <p>I have to go back to <choice>
                        <sic>rochester</sic>
                        <corr>Rochester</corr>
                    </choice> to get my discharge.</p>
                <p>the day that I left <choice>
                        <sic>thare</sic>
                        <corr>there</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <sic>avent</sic>
                        <corr>I went</corr>
                    </choice> to the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">patent
                        office</unclear> to see you but you <choice>
                            <sic>was</sic>
                            <corr>were</corr>
                        </choice> not <choice>
                        <sic>thare</sic>
                        <corr>there</corr>
                    </choice>, and I had not time to go <choice>
                        <sic>whare</sic>
                        <corr>where</corr>
                    </choice> you <choice>
                        <sic>was</sic>
                        <corr>were</corr>
                    </choice> but, <choice>
                        <sic>avent</sic>
                        <corr>I went</corr>
                    </choice> back to ward C and gave to <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low"
                        resp="#nnk">no C</unclear>
                    <choice>
                        <sic>thare</sic>
                        <corr>there</corr>
                    </choice> in the ward 70 <choice>
                        <abbr>cts</abbr>
                        <expan>cents</expan>
                    </choice> to give to you he said that he would let you have it the first
                        <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">time</unclear> that you
                    came in. Now <choice>
                        <sic>pleas</sic>
                        <corr>please</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <sic>rite</sic>
                        <corr>write</corr>
                    </choice> and let me know if you got it I wanted to see you 
                    <pb xml:id="leaf004v" facs="loc.01817.007_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                    
                    I would like
                    to <choice>
                        <sic>no</sic>
                        <corr>know</corr>
                    </choice> if you got that money anyhow. I got <gap reason="illegible"
                        extent="one word" unit="chars" quantity="6"/> two weeks ago last <unclear
                        reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">Friday</unclear>, but I find
                    myself rather weak yet last <choice>
                        <sic>friday</sic>
                        <corr>Friday</corr>
                    </choice> I was on A <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk"><choice>
                            <sic>lode</sic>
                            <corr>load</corr>
                        </choice></unclear> of hay and went to get down
                    <choice>
                        <sic>of</sic>
                        <corr>off</corr>
                    </choice> from it and I fell and <choice>
                        <sic>scard</sic>
                        <corr>scared</corr>
                    </choice> the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk"
                        >horses</unclear>
                    one them kicked me on the forehead then they start to run and the wagon wheel struck me on
                    the back of my head and <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk"
                        >hurt</unclear> me bad but can sit <choice>
                        <sic>rite</sic>
                        <corr>right</corr>
                    </choice> now. I think of <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">no
                        more</unclear> at <choice><sic>preasent</sic><corr>present</corr></choice>. <choice>
                        <sic>Pleas</sic>
                        <corr>Please</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <sic>rite</sic>
                        <corr>write</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">if</unclear> you get
                    this</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Address</salute>
                    <signed rend="center">Alfred E Pratt</signed>
                    <salute>Aug the 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> Williamson<lb/>Wayne Co.<lb/>N Y</salute>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>My friends <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">their</unclear>
                        respects <pb xml:id="leaf005v" facs="loc.01817.008_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                        <choice>
                            <sic>Pleas</sic>
                            <corr>Please</corr>
                        </choice> if get this <choice>
                            <sic>rite</sic>
                            <corr>write</corr>
                        </choice> and if you will <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk"><choice>
                                <sic>Pleas</sic>
                                <corr>Please</corr>
                            </choice> send</unclear> me that photograph of <choice>
                            <sic>abe</sic>
                            <corr>Abe</corr>
                        </choice> and Washington like yours if you can find them and I will Say I
                            glad for
                        it</p>
                </postscript>
            </div1>
            <pb xml:id="leaf006r" facs="loc.01817.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf006v" facs="loc.01817.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>

        </body>
